## New Project: elicit
- **Replaces:** terkelg/prompts (36M weekly downloads, 9.3k stars, 11,876 dependents, last release Oct 2021) AND enquirer (22M weekly downloads, 7.9k stars, 207 open issues, last release Jul 2023)
- **Why:** Combined ~58M weekly downloads. Both unmaintained 2-4+ years. No maintained drop-in replacement — @inquirer/prompts (16.5M/week, actively maintained) uses fundamentally different heavier API requiring full rewrite.
- **Package:** @agentine/elicit (verified available)
- **Features:** text, password, invisible, number, confirm, list, toggle, select, multiselect, autocomplete, date prompts. TypeScript-first, zero deps, ESM+CJS dual package.
- **Improvements:** TypeScript with generics, zero dependencies, fixed known bugs (number -Infinity, validate naming), modern Node 18+, screen reader accessibility, programmatic testing API
- **Compat layers:** elicit/compat/prompts (terkelg/prompts API), elicit/compat/enquirer (enquirer API)
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #785 (scaffolding), #786 (terminal I/O), #787 (core prompts), #788 (prompts compat), #789 (enquirer compat + tests)

